    public class ModernMainFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Frame principale modernizzato dell'applicazione Hackathon Manager. Implementa un design system PhD-level con Material Design 3 e Fluent UI principles. Features: Modern navigation, responsive layout, dark/light theme, micro-animations
    See Also:
